OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill see scattered showers. Showers
OL,7,Fgradually dying out through the early
OL,8,Fhours, becoming dry by dawn. A cold
OL,9,Fnight with frost in sheltered glens.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FDry in the morning with some
OL,12,Fearly sunshine. Dry and cloudier in
OL,13,Fthe afternoon, outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fspreading northeast in the evening
OL,15,Falong with strengthening southeasterly
OL,16,Fwinds. Rather cold.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,19,Fdry with sunny intervals and just a
OL,20,Ffew showers on Saturday. More in the
OL,21,Fway of showers on Sunday and Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
